snippet.title: Dungeons of Dreadrock 2 - The Dead King's Secret (Trailer)
snippet.description: Switch Release Nov 28th then Steam and Mobile. So far it has won DevCom Award Best Mobile and it's currently nominated for Gamescom Award Best Mobile.
